y after midnight EST and all day on Tues, Wed, Thurs...) give me a tell.  If your not a evil being and of good heart I am sure Laz will reply nicely. (If a but smugly...he IS a Erudite after all, even though he is a nice one...well it's in the blood you know...)<br><br>Thanks again for the warm welcome!  I look forward to spending more time here, if I have a good enough time, I might make a full move from MT, but leaving the Champions would be VERY hard, best RP guild I ever saw!<br><br>- Laz OOC)<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uxaviarstormburnt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xaviar Stormburnt</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/26/02 6:37:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1197.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hail and well met all!</span><hr size=1> No TLC effected items must be magical.  Good to see new faces around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uwearelegion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>We Are Legion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Cris.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/26/02 7:24:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1197.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Crissnakk.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hail and well met all!</span><hr size=1> (OOC Well that is good!  My only fear has been squashed! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I hope to meet some of you online and I have a feeling that Laz will make appearances often.  I have been trying to get some of my fellow Champions to come over on their off time to just relax and roleplay without the guild back on MT, but things are hectic now and there is no time for those who are entrenced in the guild more so then I<br><br>- Laz OOC) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uimogenelddar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ImogenElddar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/27/02 1:03:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1197.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hail and well met all!</span><hr size=1> &lt;&lt;With the TLC how doe sthat affect tradeskill items?&gt;&gt;<br><br>TLC plays merry hell with cultural armors.  All other tradeskills are unaffected by TLC as far as I know. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uartillis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 220<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/27/02 7:08:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1197.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hail and well met all!</span><hr size=1> If its LORE or MAGIC it will be effected by TLC.<br><br>So if there are some quests you want to do that require a certain magic item that you need, you might want to check into them ASAP so you don't out level it. <br><br>Take a mage and his eppic.  He needs the cloak from from a certain flying horse that is a level 30 mob.  At level 41-42 that flying beast becomes trivial and thus you can't loot any magic or lore items off it.<br><br>HOWEVER.  Almost EVERYTHING on this server is tradable.  If there is someting your used to seein on anouther server that is no drop, chances are you can buy it here.<br><br>Take my Akumen wizard only quest mask from the temple of solusek ro.  Most items from the quests from the temple are no drop on other servers.  Not this one, I can sell my mask if i choose.  It's especialy usefull with quest itmes.  I'd been having a heck of a time collecting snow griffon eggs for the 3rd coldain prayer shall, well I ended up buying 3 off someone for 450pp, normaly they are no drop.  So have fun with it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br><br>Artillis Windruss<br>Wizard of the 45th channeling<br>Follower of the Burning Prince. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uwearelegion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>We Are Legion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Cris.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/27/02 7:14:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1197.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Crissnakk.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hail and well met all!</span><hr size=1> (OOC Interesting.  Heh...sounds nice actually...also tough.  One would think that this would make a guid WANT t